  • Constructor Details

    • ListOfIcaos

      public ListOfIcaos()
      Constructs a new instance of ListOfIcaos. This class is responsible for loading and managing a list of ICAO codes and their corresponding data. The data is loaded from a CSV file located at "files/iata-icao.csv". The CSV file should contain the following columns: "country_code", "region_name", "iata", "icao", "airport", "latitude", "longitude". The loaded data is stored in the listIcaos field.
      Throws:
      RuntimeException - If an error occurs while reading the CSV file or if any required columns are missing.
